dc_title_s: Unincorporated Zoning District Boundaries: Cook County, Illinois
dc_description_s: This is a polygon dataset of Unincorporated Zoning District Boundaries (Aggregate) for Cook County, Illinois. This data is provided by the Cook County Dept. Of Building and Zoning and is maintained by the Cook County Zoning Board of Appeals._x000D_Only unincorporated district boundaries are available, please contact specific municipalities for questions regarding incorporated municipal zoning districts.
